<div class="container">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="hero-section">
    <h2>Welcome to FridgAi</h2>
    <p>Your intelligent culinary assistant</p>
  </div>

  <div class="presentation">
    <div class="intro">
      <h3>What is FridgAi?</h3>
      <p>
        FridgAi is your personal kitchen companion that transforms the ingredients
        in your fridge into delicious recipes. Thanks to our artificial
        intelligence, you'll never wonder "What should I cook today?" again.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="how-it-works">
      <h3>How does it work?</h3>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <h4>1. Add your ingredients</h4>
          <p>
            Fill your virtual fridge with all the food items and utensils
            you have available.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <h4>2. Ask for a recipe</h4>
          <p>
            Our FridgAi analyzes your fridge and suggests personalized recipes
            based on what you have.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <h4>3. Cook and enjoy!</h4>
          <p>
            Follow the instructions and savor creative dishes without food waste.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="benefits">
      <h3>Why use FridgAi?</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Personalized recipes based on your available ingredients</li>
        <li>Save money by using what you already have</li>
        <li>to stop wasting time searching for recipies</li>
        <li>Discover new recipies</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
    <div class="bottom">
      <h3>Ready to start?</h3>
      <p>
       Get started now by
       <%= link_to "Signing up", new_user_registration_path, class: "highlight-link" %>
       and start cooking with FridgAi !
      </p>
      <p>
       You already have an account ?
        <%= link_to "Log in", new_user_session_path, class: "highlight-link" %>
      </p>
    </div>
